{"tid":508870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"朱經緯將在獄中度過58歲生日（25日）及聖誕節","createTime":"2017-12-24T16:15:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-24T16:22:46.000Z","uid":5195,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"de70a94a236c2779a7bcc31a61d22bb8b9d1b189","tid":508870,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T16:15:25.000Z","msg":"退休警司朱經緯於2014年佔領行動期間，在旺角執勤時以警棍毆打途人頸部，被控一項襲擊致造成身體傷害罪，案件經審訊後，朱昨被裁定罪成，還押至12月29日判刑。朱經緯將在獄中度過58歲生日（25日）及聖誕節；其幼子聞裁決後表現激動，在庭內大罵「咩對唔住呀，打╳多佢（事主）幾下𠻹呀」（見另稿）。"},{"pid":"3fad10e349c1807cb3566e33a8292330b9df5a26","tid":508870,"uid":7323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T16:18:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">痛快</span>"},{"pid":"d551b0bd92d9572de44aa12f27935b1355fe448f","tid":508870,"uid":4574,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T16:20:40.000Z","msg":"今晚都係失身夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b48d7d10356eaa7c8f5f4e1eaedc1dc5a5c15e78","tid":508870,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T16:22:46.000Z","msg":"豬隊友都算<br />\n仲要係自己個仔"}]}